997, "(fr)If $w Koth sends in the $h Repulse to finish the job, Command will deploy the $f Colossus to strike the final blow. Your secondary objective will be to defend the $f Rampart during this phase of the battle. The cruiser will probably sustain damage from the earlier exchange. Good luck, Alpha."

