1314, "(fr)Welcome to the $w 203rd, Terran. I am $w Commander $w Habu, squadron leader. Our unit has served the Emperor since the war between our species, nearly five decades ago. I understand you were among the pilots who assisted our counter-insurgency effort in the $b Deneb system. We are honored to fight by your side, pilot. You will lead $f Alpha wing."

